       76 +## UX choices
       77 +
       78 +- The top-level company selector defaults to **All** (per spec
          +). When set to a specific company:
       79 +  - New Entries pre-fills that company on rows whose company h
          +asn't been chosen yet (never overwrites a manual selection).
       80 +  - History narrows to that company's entries.
       81 +- Per-row validation errors render inline with red borders and
          + a one-line message under the field.
       82 +- Tab moves through fields in the spec order (Company → Date →
          + Employee → Project → Task → Hours).
       83 +- `⌘D` / `Ctrl+D` duplicates the last row; `⌘Enter` / `Ctrl+En
          +ter` submits.
       84 +- Each row has explicit "Duplicate" and "Remove" buttons for m
          +ouse users.
