       86 +## Performance notes
       87 +
       88 +- Lookup endpoints (`employees`, `projects`, `tasks`) are scop
          +ed per company so payloads stay small even with many companies
          +.
       89 +- The frontend caches lookup responses in-memory for the lifet
          +ime of the page (`composables/useApi.js`). Concurrent rows ope
          +ning the same company share a single in-flight request via a p
          +romise cache.
       90 +- `time_entries` carries indexes on `(employee_id, date)` for
          +the business-rule lookup and `(company_id, date)` for history
          +filtering.
       91 +- The list endpoint eager-loads all four belongs-to relations
          +to avoid N+1.
       92 +- For larger datasets, the History endpoint should add paginat
          +ion (`paginate(50)`) and the dropdowns should switch to typeah
          +ead/search. Stubbed for now to keep the surface small.
